ğŸ“Œ Left Section: Four Key Phases
1ï¸âƒ£ Phase Division â€“ EEG data is divided into different time segments for better analysis of seizure progression.
2ï¸âƒ£ Pre-feature Extraction â€“ Raw EEG signals are processed using Fourier Transform (FFT) to extract frequency-domain features.
3ï¸âƒ£ CNN Feature Extraction â€“ Deep learning is used to automatically learn patterns from EEG signals.
4ï¸âƒ£ SVM Classification â€“ A Support Vector Machine classifier is applied for the final classification of seizure states.

